data.description: SELLER OFFERING $10,000 BUYER CREDIT with acceptable offer.  PRIME LOCATION South of I10 close to Duke FLD, 7th SFG, Eglin AFB and Hurlburt FLD.  4th Bedroom is a flex room currently being used as an office, but can easily be converted back by adding doors.  This beautiful home has New kitchen cabinets, New granite countertops, New SS appliances, New LVP flooring and carpet throughout, New granite in bathrooms, New HWH, the entire house has been repainted including the floor boards, Metal roof 2022, New window blinds and the list goes on and on. It even has an enclosed sun porch that you can enjoy all year around. The property also has a fully fenced in backyard and a 30AMP RV hookup in the garage.
